  <brief_title>Endometrial Safety Study of a 0.5 mg Estradiol and 2.5 mg Dydrogesterone Combination</brief_title>
  <official_title>Endometrial Safety of a Low Dose Continuous Combined 17 -Estradiol/Dydrogesterone Hormone Replacement Regimen (E2 0.5 mg/ D 2.5 mg) in Postmenopausal Women - A One-Year, Open Label, Multi-Center Study</official_title>
